name: r-randtests
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.0.1" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-randtests
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/randtests_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/randtests/randtests_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 479558010cc7aa44d83bfa51d35f8f1d814958e405408f71395a539c9e392be4

build:
  noarch: generic
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:

  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('randtests')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('randtests')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=randtests
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: Several non parametric randomness tests for numeric sequences
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
